3Com Corp said itintroduced a new network workstation for business applications.    The product, called 3Station, is the first in a family ofnetwork workstations, which will later include a Token Ringversion, the company said.    It said the 3Station is an IBM-compatible 80286-basedEthernet product which can be integrated with personalcomputers on a network.    The company also said it plans to begin shipments on May15. Reuter&#3;